  "description": "A BIDS-converted fNIRS neuroimaging dataset containing time-series hemoglobin data from 18 subjects across two sessions with ICA denoising applied. The dataset includes standardized NIRS JSON sidecars with acquisition parameters (sampling frequency, channel count, source/detector mapping) and is provided in SNIRF format to facilitate reproducibility and data sharing. This dataset was converted from MATLAB format (TimeSeriesHbORT_18sub_twoSessionICAdenoise) using automated conversion tools.",
